# Basic Supervised Workflow
# 
# Global SUPERVISED at the top enables supervision for all steps.
# The supervisor monitors execution and auto-corrects if drift is detected.

SUPERVISED
NAME basic-supervised

INPUT topic DEFAULT "renewable energy trends"

# Define agents
AGENT researcher "Research the given topic thoroughly. Find current data, trends, and key insights." -> findings, sources
AGENT analyst "Analyze findings and identify patterns, opportunities, and risks." -> analysis, recommendations

# Define goals
GOAL research "Research $topic and compile findings" -> research_output USING researcher
GOAL analyze "Analyze research findings and provide recommendations" -> final_analysis USING analyst

# Execution
RUN research_phase USING research
RUN analysis_phase USING analyze
